{"tid":1164621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你班盲撐Bob叔嘅撚樣可唔可以理性少少？","createTime":"2019-05-21T08:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T07:07:01.000Z","uid":75264,"like":25,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c86ea5ce9b19b9c5257b199a5477f11978a960","tid":1164621,"uid":75264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"其實個班反慕容係咪想無視bob叔老屈人？<br />\n成條片個起點就係講緊佢一直追擊不斷抹黑慕容<br />\n身為有影響力既youtuber係網絡上用唔同平台抹黑其他youtuber係冇錯？<br />\n同埋條片最後都總結咗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">技能</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人脈</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">背景有錢</span></span> <br />\n以上三樣嘢都冇就一定要有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學歷</span></span>去支持你個人<br />\n我想問你班盲反撚解釋以上幾點有邊樣講得唔啱？<br />\n重點野就唔提 就係度講其他讀書唔讀書呢啲咁主觀嘅野<br />\n仲要大部份人都係圍繞住學歷呢樣野嚟講<br />\n先入為主認定佢因為冇學歷 所以講啲Point再有道理都係錯<br />\n而bob叔就係因為係外國留學 就唔理點都信咗大半先<br />\n呢啲叫批判思考？ <br />\n即係同你講如果兩邊都有持有大學學位 你地係咪會自相矛盾click死自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話咩唔想睇條片比view佢 唔睇都知佢係廢噏 覺得佢有道理嘅人一定係讀唔成書 呢啲叫理性討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身住Hall自己煮嘢都係睇開bob叔啲片多 間中先會睇下慕容啲講經片<br />\n原本真係食吓花生笑吓算尻數<br />\n但睇完啲留言發覺你班柒碌真係連作為成年人既分析能力都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要覺得自己係好有道理 就係因為有bob叔呢個你地口中所講讀得成書嘅人做你地後台<br />\n明眼人就分辨到留言嘅人邊啲就係社會上嘅踏腳石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302ac3b00223f01e03af400af65e088fc46335e1","tid":1164621,"uid":23486,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"咁我想問香港地有幾多人係有曬技能 人脈 同 背景有錢呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你又唔係唔知條無用公仔主要target audience係班小學雞<br />\n佢地仲細唔識諗<br />\n萬一佢地on99咁以為自己識幾個朋友就當有人脈就走去唔讀書<br />\n佢地呢一生就真係多得你唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01664dcbc3b006b00afe416acc8c0a2a13f34be4","tid":1164621,"uid":75264,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"302ac3b00223f01e03af400af65e088fc46335e1","tid":1164621,"uid":23486,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"咁我想問香港地有幾多人係有曬技能 人脈 同 背景有錢呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你又唔係唔知條無用公仔主要target audience係班小學雞<br />\n佢地仲細唔識諗<br />\n萬一佢地on99咁以為自己識幾個朋友就當有人脈就走去唔讀書<br />\n佢地呢一生就真係多得你唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"其實你係咪閱讀理解有問題 技能 人脈 同 背景有錢 <br />\n只要你有其中一樣都已經係可以唔使靠學歷都搵到錢<br />\n三樣都冇你就一定要靠學歷"},{"pid":"9969b0ebacc1c40b4e10b73a6f27a2d1809f4bc2","tid":1164621,"uid":185038,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:12:26.000Z","msg":"樓主走先 我幫你頂住!<br />\n理性討論係連登唔work架!走啦!"},{"pid":"4a66d18c9c09a09c84bfdd2e5b3101994996b267","tid":1164621,"uid":23364,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:13:33.000Z","msg":"先唔理bob叔 <br />\n<br />\n垃圾公子收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874ba3125f293cff2c0bb7133b77e533b237254e","tid":1164621,"uid":83166,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"佢用倫敦金同埋ptgf 做例子 你自己覺得有冇問題"},{"pid":"897417c167737cb0e7c6f7e584c57ecda3108550","tid":1164621,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"撐bob叔！我地有學識有文化,思路正確！唔撐bob叔都係社會垃圾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1163996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1163996</a>"},{"pid":"2283edf0f025ae5b009ad5222a3de284a8a49b83","tid":1164621,"uid":86027,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"你唔讀書去邊度學啲技能返黎<br />\n你本身冇家底唔靠讀書點解識啲比較上流既人脈返黎"},{"pid":"ad6f07e0bd839bdd0fac432122af87a6c9e6fcb2","tid":1164621,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"要幾柒先會為左自己偶像屌鳩其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依件事既結局就係兩個人出黎飲餐茶冰釋前嫌"},{"pid":"389de41015c2294e8406c601aa04a43f40d6f9fc","tid":1164621,"uid":139671,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"其實睇返bob叔真係好多point都自打嘴巴，又雙重標準，好多point都好矛盾<br />\n<br />\n相反以point駁point黎講，慕容公子真係回覆得比較全面同有論點好多，啲唔知咩事既觀眾好容易比慕容公子吸引走去支持佢"},{"pid":"9d00590a6fe97289ed45fc4fce64297d3f4463d1","tid":1164621,"uid":120361,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"你係咪學識太低聽唔明？人地係話咩圈子識咩人呀懵丙。喺大學識返高學歷嘅人有乜問題？你可以唔讀書識到教授？"},{"pid":"ccc1e497c6b9efd37fba3dcc2f11ff94eba42984","tid":1164621,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"你死喇，夠膽話連登仔契爺"},{"pid":"d2bcd4428fc1e48ec07ec2308c07b9f79e916c66","tid":1164621,"uid":185038,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d00590a6fe97289ed45fc4fce64297d3f4463d1","tid":1164621,"uid":120361,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"你係咪學識太低聽唔明？人地係話咩圈子識咩人呀懵丙。喺大學識返高學歷嘅人有乜問題？你可以唔讀書識到教授？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"你真係on9仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高學歷一定要係大學識?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫你理性討論你就入黎話人學識低懵丙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學識高既話咁你小學常識阿sir有冇教你以事論事啊小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6d16710bf0753711d21b31a812d7852308b7e9","tid":1164621,"uid":26106,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:39:49.000Z","msg":"如果龜頭bob個外表係慕容個mk樣<br />\nd人就反龜頭bob嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兒登仔不嬲鐘意搬龍門<br />\n其他香港人大陸人炒樓就咒人仆街死，推高樓價<br />\n龜頭bob炒樓就係精明專業投資<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似呢個po咁<br />\n先唔理內容係咪真<br />\n但成班連登仔就屌個老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話讀書緊要過技能<br />\n<br />\n小六男生愛煮飯成績包尾　媽媽崩潰求助心理學家：他數學只考1分<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1164410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1164410</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b7225d4f6140dd795d0f8f9661c0d562e79db50","tid":1164621,"uid":54574,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"想問下各位連登仔，龜頭bob條鳩好唔好味？個個奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a80facbcd9c92334eb7a99ff97622163867017","tid":1164621,"uid":185709,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"咁多point自打嘴巴都仲要撐？<br />\nBob叔專心煮下野食拍下vlog好過啦"},{"pid":"bb9adb31120afebe6f37857b51e241c493df523a","tid":1164621,"uid":26106,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b7225d4f6140dd795d0f8f9661c0d562e79db50","tid":1164621,"uid":54574,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"想問下各位連登仔，龜頭bob條鳩好唔好味？個個奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"明明平時最憎炒樓撚，父幹撚 <br />\n只係個樣生得似懷仔就捧上神台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8647f716c011d8a0015eba9039176bfd8cfe6c2f","tid":1164621,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JTUJUqu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJTUJUqu.gif&h=aabb2c04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"874c5de00211e162e92859a5c602aec63e07a767","tid":1164621,"uid":26106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be6d16710bf0753711d21b31a812d7852308b7e9","tid":1164621,"uid":26106,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy"